EffectCategory::CompareCategories

EffectCategory::CompareCategories Struct Reference

#include <EffectCategory.h>

List of all members.

Detailed Description

This is used in the CategorySet typedef. It compares category pointers, first by their names and then by pointer values. This makes CategorySets automatically sorted by name while allowing for different categories with the same name.
